BTC/USDT historical data

Source: R/data-btcusdt.R
btcusdt.Rd

BTC/USDT historical data

data(btcusdt)

Format

An object of class tibble.

Source

KuCoin market's API.

Details

This historical data is obtained from KuCoin market's API, which queried using rucoin. The dataset is ranging from May 1, 2019 to July 31, 2019, and contains following informations:

  • datetime

  • open

  • high

  • low

  • close

  • volume

  • turnover

Examples


# import library
library(quantrecipes)

# print the data
btcusdt
